@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<div class="text-center" id="about-wrapper">
    <div id="about-first-wrapper">
        <h1 class="display-4">About Chrun</h1>
        <p class="about-p">Chrun is a Canadian company that specializes in aggregating financial and credit product information for users. Our platform provides a comprehensive range of products and services to help individuals make informed decisions about their financial needs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content-wrapper">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="about-p">At Chrun, our mission is to empower Canadians with the knowledge and tools they need to navigate the complex world of finance. We believe that everyone deserves access to reliable and unbiased information to make informed financial decisions.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content-wrapper">
        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <p class="about-p">Chrun offers a user-friendly platform that allows you to compare and explore various financial and credit products, including:</p>

        <ul id="about-ul">
            <li>Mortgages</li>
            <li>Personal Loans</li>
            <li>Credit Cards</li>
            <li>Accounts</li>
            <li>Insurance</li>
            <li>and more</li>
        </ul>
       
    </div>

    <div class="about-content-wrapper">
        <h2>How We Work</h2>
        <p class="about-p">Chrun uses advanced data analytics to aggregate information from various financial institutions and lenders. We present the information in a clear and concise manner, allowing you to easily compare and evaluate different options.</p>

        <p class="about-p">Our team of experts diligently researches and analyzes the market to provide up-to-date and accurate information on different products, interest rates, terms, and eligibility criteria. We strive to simplify the process of finding the right financial solutions tailored to your needs and act as an intermediary to direct purchase of products.</p>


        <p class="about-p">Whether you're looking to refinance your mortgage, find a suitable credit card, or explore investment opportunities, Chrun is here to guide you through the process. We aim to provide an intuitive and transparent experience that helps you make confident financial decisions.</p>
    </div>


    <div class="about-content-wrapper">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="about-p">If you have any questions, feedback, or partnership inquiries, please don't hesitate to <a href="/contact">contact us</a>. We value your input and are always striving to improve our platform to better serve our users.</p>
    </div>
</div>
